configFileTemplateContent:
global:
  scrape_interval: 15s
  evaluation_interval: 15s
alerting:
  alertmanagers:
    - static_configs:
      - targets:
rule_files:
scrape_configs:
<#list Targets as target>
  - job_name: '${target.jobName}':
    static_configs:
    - targets: ['${target.ipAddress}']
    - labels: ['${target.label}']
</#list>'
